<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Children=E2=80=99s Place was a popular sto=
ck, it put out terrible results, the shareholders rushed to sell, and Mitha=
q swooped in to buy. Most of the shareholders wanted to sell, so it could g=
et the stock cheap, and they wanted to sell=C2=A0<em>immediately</em>, so i=
t could get the stock fast.=C2=A0Now it owns the company. Maybe it can fix =
it? It will be a weird ride for the holders of the other 46%.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is one immediate problem, which is that =
by buying a majority of the stock Mithaq has triggered a default on the com=
pany=E2=80=99s credit agreement. =E2=80=9CAs a result of Mithaq=E2=80=99s s=
