<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Shares of SoundHound AI and Nano-X Imaging jum=
ped Thursday after chip giant Nvidia disclosed stakes in the companies.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">SoundHound, which specializes in voice-enabled=
 artificial intelligence, was recently up 50%. Shares of Nano-X, an Israel-=
based medical imaging company, were up more than 65%.</p>
