<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a bank with a private banking busin=
ess for wealthy clients, the two main things that you want from your privat=
e bankers are:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You want them to serve their clients=
=E2=80=99 needs, put the clients first and=C2=A0make the=C2=A0clients feel =
well taken care of,=C2=A0so the clients stick with your bank, add more asse=
ts to the relationship, and recommend your services to their friends.</li>=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You want them to extract more=C2=A0<em=
>revenue=C2=A0</em>from the clients, by upselling and cross-selling them on=
 new products that earn money for your bank.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Are these goals in conflict with each other? O=
h, sure, absolutely, a lot of the time: Often the best way to take care of =
clients is=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0</em>by putting them into a lot of high-fee pr=
oducts that are good for the bank. But there really is a lot of overlap. Of=
ten the clients=C2=A0<em>do=C2=A0</em>want a loan, or a fancy private inves=
tment vehicle, and setting them up with one is both good client service and=
 good revenue generation. A good private banker will do both things seamles=
sly; the clients will happily pay the bank lots of money, because they feel=
 like they=E2=80=99re getting good value.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a really=C2=A0<em>big=C2=A0</em>ban=
k with a private banking business, you will hire hundreds of private banker=
s and let them loose on thousands of clients and=C2=A0<em>tell=C2=A0</em>th=
em to do those things, but you will have a hard time <em>measuring</em> the=
m. Good customer service can be approximated with anecdotal feedback, surve=
ys, data on churn, etc., but you won=E2=80=99t have perfect visibility into=
 how good each banker is at customer service. Revenue is easier to measure,=
 but also somewhat random =E2=80=94=C2=A0some bankers will have clients who=
 inherit fortunes and need more products, through no effort of the banker =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0and it=E2=80=99s harder to measure who is good at=C2=A0<em>t=
rying=C2=A0</em>to generate revenue.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And so you might implement some <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34364292.279392/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
ZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvOGQwNDFmZDQtZDU2Yy00MmZhLWFkMTYtNjk3YTJjYTA5Njgx/607f07=
ceef4b8524a319a23cBaeca4b05" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope"=
 target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importan=
t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> incredibly crude metric</a> to decide=
 which bankers are doing a good job of serving customers and pitching produ=
cts:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Citigroup has started tracking how many calls =
its private bankers are making to clients as the US lender tries to jump-st=
art its struggling wealth management business, according to people familiar=
 with the matter.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Citi=E2=80=99s private bankers must now turn i=
n call reports to record each conversation they have with a client =E2=80=
=94 whose net worth typically has to be at least $10mn to qualify for the p=
rivate bank =E2=80=94 and also what was discussed, the people said.=C2=A0</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">They have also been encouraged to contact each=
 of their clients at least once every 90 days, the people added. =E2=80=A6<=
/p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The requirement had been badly received by som=
e employees, who felt it was not a productive use of their time, the people=
 familiar with the matter said. It also comes as Citi is cutting thousands =
of jobs as part of big reorganisation.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A Citi spokesperson said: =E2=80=9CEnhancing c=
lient experience is our number-one focus. Documenting and sharing client fe=
edback is one way to ensure we=E2=80=99re delivering for them, and is a sta=
ndard practice within Citi and across the industry.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
